  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375\u00b0F (190\u00b0C). Rinse quinoa under cold water and cook according to package instructions.",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine cooked quinoa with chickpeas, onions, garlic, tomatoes, cumin seeds, coriander powder, turmeric powder, salt, and oil. Mix well until all ingredients are evenly distributed.",
